OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBraverman wants to curb use
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fof tents by homeless       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The home secretary is proposing new    
OL,6, laws to restrict the use of tents by   
OL,7, homeless people, arguing that many of  
OL,8, them see it as a lifestyle choice.     
OL,10,FSuella Braverman's plan would introduce
OL,11,Fnew penalties in England and Wales for 
OL,12,Fhomeless people whom authorities       
OL,13,Fbelieve have rejected offers of help.  
OL,15,FBritain "cannot allow our streets to be
OL,16,Ftaken over by rows of tents," she said.
OL,18,FHousing charity Shelter responded that 
OL,19,F"nobody should be punished for being   
OL,20,Fhomeless".                             
